<div class="column">
<div>
<h1>Goal Talk Podcast Episode 15: Updates on Marketing During COVID-19—Data, Reactivation, &amp; More</h1>
</div>
</div>
<div class="column">
<div></div>
</div>
<div class="column">
<div class="field-item">
<div class="text text--grey"><label class="label"><br />
Last updated: </label><br />
May 26, 2020</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="column">
<div>
<div class="tag">
<div class="tag__text">WordStream</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="column">
<div>
<p>On each episode of this season of the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/goal-talk?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=">Goal Talk podcast</a>, I interview a marketing or management expert to bring small business owners and marketers the information they need to successfully <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/growth-academy">grow</a> their businesses.</p>
<p>It’s been two full weeks since we’ve had an episode of the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/goal-talk?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=">Goal Talk podcast</a>, and while we’re embracing our updated bi-weekly episode release schedule, we missed releasing an episode last week! So it only felt right to bring a guest <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/04/21/goal-talk-episode-11">back onto the podcast</a> this week to bring an update on the state of digital marketing during COVID-19 for advertisers.</p>
<h2>This week: Current updates on COVID-19 marketing tips, performance data, and account reactivation</h2>
<p>Last time we had <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/mark-irvine-42">Mark</a> on the podcast, we discussed the preliminary data around how the social effects of social distancing and mandatory business practice modifications have impacted digital marketing for advertisers. That <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/04/21/goal-talk-episode-11">episode</a> was released about a month ago as we were navigating the first few weeks of the majority of the effects of the pandemic worldwide. In the episode, we discussed how search trends and patterns are shifting, some options for small business assistance from the government, and the data around how the mandated changes have impacted the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/03/18/covid-19-google-ads-data">PPC results</a> for multiple industries.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.embed_image_narrow" data-entity-embed-display-settings="https://www.wordstream.com/goal-talk?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="4f42fa09-67da-41f4-8cfe-497e6122101b" data-langcode="en">
<article>
<div><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Goal-Talk-Ep14-Square_0.png" alt="Goal Talk podcast episode 15 artwork." width="800" height="800" /></div>
</article>
</div>
<p>This week, we have more information—including more data—about how the long-term effects of COVID-19 are playing out for a variety of advertisers. With strong signals of a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/05/04/ppc-rebound-covid-19-data">rebound</a> in the PPC results for advertisers in many industries, this episode discusses the options advertisers have for reading their own data and working towards <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/05/06/google-ads-account-recovery">reactivating their accounts</a> for continued success.</p>
<p>In today’s <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/goal-talk?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=">episode</a>, we discuss:</p>
<ul>
<li>Updates on the current state of search.</li>
<li>How search marketing has changed in the past month and new results for advertisers.</li>
<li>Tips for marketers during their reactivation efforts.</li>
<li>Signals for advertisers to look for in their accounts.</li>
<li>How advertisers can fuel their reopening plans with their cross-channel marketing efforts.</li>
</ul>
<p>And more!</p>
<p>You can find this week’s episode on <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/goal-talk-podcast/id1497955409">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/7BnP53IsIOkydFl1qPKD7E">Spotify</a>, as well as your favorite podcast app. Also, don’t forget to watch new episodes on our <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrvBaHMLtSQ55IWAZiRQuQQ">YouTube channel</a>, and follow the podcast’s <a href="https://twitter.com/goaltalkpodcast">Twitter</a> account for episode releases to ask the hosts questions and to join in on the conversation.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="videos" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.embed_video" data-entity-embed-display-settings="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OdCXqPYcUb8&amp;feature=youtu.be" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="14f329d9-cd24-4a75-b7ab-0e4fb0abc8b0" data-langcode="en">
<article>
<div>
<div class="video-embed-field-provider-youtube video-embed-field-responsive-video"><iframe width="854" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OdCXqPYcUb8?autoplay=0&amp;start=0&amp;rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<h2>About the podcast</h2>
<p>The<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/goal-talk?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content="> Goal Talk podcast</a> is all about giving small business owners and marketers the information they need to succeed. From advertising tactics that help you personalize your message for your customers to management styles that will help your employees perform at their full potential and feel satisfied in their role, we’re sharing valuable takeaways to help you and your business flourish by interviewing the experts and sharing their insights. <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/goal-talk?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=">Listen here.</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="column">
<div class="views-element-container contextual-region"></div>
</div>
</div>
